reviewText: I was very pleased with my purchase.  The order was on time and exactly as represented.  It was a pleasure for me to have such a good turnaround.
What would Jesus look like and sound like if we could see Him today? I more than enjoyed the DVDs and really want to share them with others>

My wife and I watched this and really enjoyed it. We had checked it out from our church's library, but now plan to buy it. We were both very impressed with the story line and the quality of the movie.
